  {http://ryantm.github.io/nixpkgs/builders/special/mkshell/}[Docs].

* Args
  - `name` - name for the shell.
  - `packages` - packages to include into the environment.
  - `inputsFrom` - packages, that will have their build dependencies included in the environment.
  - `shellHook` - `.bashrc` essentially.
